Played on three occasions between 1956 and 1976 by Brazil, Argentina, Uruguay
and Paraguay (as an invited team).  Because of the participating teams this
was the most important of all the minor South American tournaments.

Year   Winner

1956   Brazil
1960   Brazil
1976   Brazil

Number of titles

Brazil      3


Copa del Atlántico 1956

24 Jun Rio de Janeiro     Brazil    2-0 Uruguay
 1 Jul Montevideo         Uruguay   1-2 Argentina
 8 Jul Buenos Aires       Argentina 0-0 Brazil

Final Table:

 1.Brazil          2  1  1  0  2- 0  3
 2.Argentina       2  1  1  0  2- 1  3
 3.Uruguay         2  0  0  2  1- 4  0

Match Details

NB: in parallel to this edition, a club tournament was held.


Copa del Atlántico 1960

