       Montevideo         Uruguay   1-0 Brazil
12 Jul Rio de Janeiro     Brazil    5-1 Argentina
13 Jul Montevideo         Uruguay   2-1 Paraguay
17 Aug Buenos Aires       Argentina 4-0 Uruguay

Final Table:

 1.Brazil          3  2  0  1  7- 3  4
 2.Argentina       3  2  0  1  6- 5  4
 3.Uruguay         3  2  0  1  3- 5  4
 4.Paraguay        3  0  0  3  2- 5  0

Match Details


Copa del Atlántico 1976

25 Feb Asunción           Paraguay  2-3 Argentina
       Montevideo         Uruguay   1-2 Brazil
27 Feb Buenos Aires       Argentina 1-2 Brazil
10 Mar Montevideo         Uruguay   2-2 Paraguay
 7 Apr Asunción           Paraguay  1-1 Brazil
 8 Apr Buenos Aires       Argentina 4-1 Uruguay
28 Apr Rio de Janeiro     Brazil    2-1 Uruguay
       Buenos Aires       Argentina 2-2 Paraguay
19 May Rio de Janeiro     Brazil    2-0 Argentina
       Asunción           Paraguay  1-0 Uruguay
 9 Jun Montevideo         Uruguay   0-3 Argentina
       Rio de Janeiro     Brazil    3-1 Paraguay

Final Table:

 1.Brazil          6  5  1  0 12- 5 11
 2.Argentina       6  3  1  2 13- 9  7
 3.Paraguay        6  1  3  2  9-11  5
 4.Uruguay         6  0  1  5  5-14  1

Match Details

NB: matches between Argentina and Paraguay also counted for the 
    Copa Félix Bogado 1976;
    matches between Argentina and Brazil also counted for the
    Copa Julio Roca 1976;
    first match between Argentina and Uruguay also counted for
    the Copa Lipton 1976;
    second match between Argentina and Uruguay also counted for
    the Copa Newton 1976;
    matches between Brazil and Uruguay also counted for the
    Copa Río Branco 1976;
    matches between Brazil and Paraguay also counted for the
    Copa Oswaldo Cruz 1976.



